# Unrestricted Repo Editing

The project owner has explicitly authorized changes across the entire repo.

## Allowed

- `client/` (web app)
- `server/` (API/backend)
- `shared/`
- build configs, migrations, and any other project files

Do **not** ask for permission to modify `client/` in future tasks.
